  "title": "MECHANICAL HEAD",
  "description": "<p>This is a newly created role and we are looking for candidate who has start-up experience in Ship Repair Mechanical functions.</p><p><u><strong>Job responsibilities</strong></u></p><ul><li>Leading the team of mechanical technicians and common contractors workers</li><li>Oversees and support the execution of ship repair mechanical projects</li><li>Set up and train the mechanical team of technicians to establish an effective, flexible and reliable support base</li></ul><p><u><strong>Job requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>GCE 'O' level or at least 5years of supervisory with start-up experience in Ship Repair industry</li><li>Must be comfortable to work in shipyard environment</li><li>Candidate with relevant working experience will be preferred</li></ul>",
